#US #COVID19 #vaccine Vaccine update for US for 3/19.

Now up to 152.4MM doses shipped to states.  This is up 17MM doses in just 8 days, no thanks to JNJ shipments.

Looks like first signs of waning demand, as many of the lowest %used are in the SE US.
